constraints.search: ( ( index=_audit sourcetype=audittrail action=search search_id=* search=* ) OR ( index=_internal sourcetype=scheduler app=* ) OR ( index=_introspection sourcetype=splunk_resource_usage component=PerProcess "data.process_type"=search "data.search_props.app"=* ) )

calculations.expression: IF(ISNULL(search) OR search="" OR match(trim(trim(search, "'")), "^\s*\|?\s*summarize") OR len(search) < 5, NULL(), trim(trim(search, "'")) )
IF( (ISNULL(savedsearch_name) OR savedsearch_name="" OR match(savedsearch_name, "\*") OR match(search, "^\| summarize") OR match(search_id, "^ta_\d+|^\d+") ), "Undefined", savedsearch_name)
IF ( ( ISNULL(roles) OR roles="") OR match(roles, "="), NULL(), trim(roles, "'"))

case ( 
      match(search_id, "^SummaryDirector") OR match(search_id, "^summarize_SummaryDirector") OR (match(savedsearch_name, "^_ACCELERATE_") AND NOT match(savedsearch_name, "^_ACCELERATE_DM_")), "report_acceleration",
      ( match(search_id, "^DM_") OR match(savedsearch_name, "^_ACCELERATE_DM_") ), "datamodel_acceleration",
      match(search_id, "^scheduler_") AND isnotnull(savedsearch_name) AND NOT match(savedsearch_name, "^_ACCELERATE_"), "scheduled", 
      match(search_id, "^rt_"), "realtime", 
      match(search_id, "^subsearch_"), "subsearch", 
      match(search_id, "^ta_\d+"), "typeahead", 
      true(), "adhoc")
if(isnull(savedsearch_name) OR savedsearch_name="" OR savedsearch_name="*", "Undefined", savedsearch_name)

CASE ( 
    status2=="continued", "deferred",
    status2=="delegated", "delegated",
    status2=="delegated_scheduled", "delegated_scheduled",
    status2=="delegated_remote", "delegated_remote",
    status2=="delegated_remote_completion", "delegated_remote_completion",
    status2=="delegated_remote_error", "delegated_remote_error",
    status2=="delegated_waiting", "delegated_waiting",
    status2=="dispatched", "dispatched",
    status2=="max_pending", "max_pending",
    status2=="max_running", "max_running",
    status2=="skipped", "skipped",
    status2=="success", "completed",
    TRUE(), status2 )

case ( 
    match(alert_actions, "summary_index"), "summary_indexing",
    match(search_type, "scheduled"), "scheduled",
    match(search_type, "datamodel_acceleration"), "datamodel_acceleration",
    (search_id LIKE "DM_%" OR savedsearch_name LIKE "_ACCELERATE_DM%"), "datamodel_acceleration", 
    savedsearch_name LIKE "_ACCELERATE_DM%", "datamodel_acceleration",
    match(search_type, "report_acceleration"), "report_acceleration",
    match(search_id, "^scheduler__") OR match(search_id, "^scheduler__") , "scheduled",
    search_id LIKE "rt%", "realtime",
    search_id LIKE "subsearch%", "subsearch",
    (search_id LIKE "SummaryDirector%" OR search_id LIKE "summarize_SummaryDirector%"), "summary_director",
    true(), "adhoc")

case ( isnotnull('data.search_props.search_head') AND 'data.search_props.role' == "peer", 'data.search_props.search_head', 
    isnull('data.search_props.search_head') AND 'data.search_props.role' == "head", "_self", 
    isnull('data.search_props.search_head') AND 'data.search_props.role' == "peer", "_unknown")

case ( 
    match('data.search_props.type', "ad-hoc"), "adhoc",
    match('data.search_props.type', "datamodel acceleration"), "datamodel_acceleration",
    match('data.search_props.type', "report acceleration"), "report_acceleration",
    match('data.search_props.type', "summary index"), "summary_indexing",
    true(), 'data.search_props.type')
